content.text:
We would now like you to complete a task that
measures how people pay attention.
This task takes about 12 minutes to complete.

For this task, a series of digits from 1 to 9 will appear
in the center of your screen. Your task is to press
the SPACEBAR every time a digit appears,  
EXCEPT when that digit is a 3. Please give equal
importance to accuracy and speed when completing this task.

Occasionally, a couple of questions will appear on the screen.
Please answer these questions quickly and honestly.
You will use the number keys to answer these questions.

Press Enter to continue.
